This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image generation. Additionally, it may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it involves generating realistic images. The use of deep learning techniques such as generative adversarial networks (GANs) suggests that it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
